snippet.title: [E3 2010] DanceMasters
snippet.description:
Being the pioneer of the franchise that started the dance game craze Konami introduces a brand new way to experience music and rhythm. The next generation in full body dancing is finally here! DanceMasters utilizes Kinect for Xbox 360 to give gamers the ultimate dance club right in their living rooms, with no peripherals required!

ESRB Rating: EVERYONE 10+ with Lyrics, Suggestive Themes
